This Java 9 tutorial Skill has been prepared for the beginners to help them understand 
the basic to advanced concepts related to Java Nine Programming language.

To launch, just say -- Alexa, open Java Nine

Main commands:
1. Alexa, ask, java nine features 
2. Alexa, ask, what is jshell
3. Alexa, ask, http two client
4. Alexa, ask, why java named Oak
5. Alexa, ask, java version history 

You can stop, help, repeat and also start from beginning as well. Commands are:
1. Alexa, stop
2. Alexa, help
3. Alexa, repeat
4. Alexa, start from beginning or Alexa, start over
